{"tid":1972318,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"叔一燒傍邊爆粗市民最終被控公眾地方行為不檢。","createTime":"2020-04-14T12:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T12:58:00.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cfd7e8ffa0922739079372dc8e4c0fab938c7580","tid":1972318,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:30:49.000Z","msg":"WAVE Broadcasting Channel （WBC）<br />\ntSpolns1or hoerSdti &middot;<br />\n<br />\n【馬鞍山男子被燒案 夫妻在旁講粗口被控公眾地方行為不檢】<br />\n<br />\n去年11月11日馬鞍山，一名男子與黑衣人在馬鞍山廣場對開行人天橋發生爭執，其間男子被人淋潑不明液體及點火，隨即燒傷，送院治理。事隔一周，警方拘捕一對夫婦，控告他們旁觀爭執事件期間講粗口，作出擾亂秩序的行動。<br />\n<br />\n案件今日在東區裁判法院繼續提堂，控方完成調查，並修訂控罪，控告他們在公眾地方行為不檢。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至6月9日1430東區裁判法院再訊，期間以原有條件繼續保釋。<br />\n<br />\n#hongkong #wavebroadcastingchannel #wavebc #wbc<br />\nFacebook: @Wavebroadcasingchannel<br />\nInstagram: @wave.bc<br />\nTwitter: waveBC<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">狗賊被影到講左咁多次粗口，連訓斥都無呀</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4e9a0e5fa48ea3d0451155ce81f984791c13e88d","tid":1972318,"uid":15644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:31:30.000Z","msg":"Omdb"},{"pid":"8dd212f60faff793a204ae612b62f031baab06cf","tid":1972318,"uid":194326,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:32:00.000Z","msg":"講粗口都要俾人拉其實都幾得人驚"},{"pid":"4d7a6797c9ecfeb442d0d463a5e3255f75b105be","tid":1972318,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:32:19.000Z","msg":"就黎可以幫佢地出書出專輯"},{"pid":"f4e1d967dc2a06caa4ff11147614349e18850611","tid":1972318,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:32:22.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c6dc0a485f6bd4ecf271e2fd7ff4708eeafdb0","tid":1972318,"uid":347130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score